28:22.657 --> 28:25.258
Let me walk you
to your front door.

28:25.260 --> 28:29.365
It gets really dangerous
here at night, sometimes.

28:33.035 --> 28:34.938
OK.

28:37.038 --> 28:38.907
Hold on,
hold on.

28:54.056 --> 28:55.625
Thank you.

29:14.710 --> 29:17.143
