about the trial.

32:41.250 --> 32:43.883
Honestly, I don't know
anything about that, really.

32:43.885 --> 32:47.222
Um, I'd be more interested in
what you've been doing since.

32:49.724 --> 32:51.490
I really liked
your novel.

32:51.492 --> 32:53.192
You read my book?

32:53.194 --> 32:55.862
Yes. It's
really, um...

32:55.864 --> 32:57.796
Hey, Chris!
How's it going, man?

32:57.798 --> 32:58.797
All right.

32:58.799 --> 33:00.366
- The usual?
- Yep!

33:00.368 --> 33:02.635
Got something for you.
