33:24.893 --> 33:26.927
I remember
when I was 24.

33:26.929 --> 33:28.795
It all seemed to
make sense.

33:28.797 --> 33:32.399
My whole life ahead of me,
my whole fucking life.

33:32.401 --> 33:33.699
What are you doing?

33:33.701 --> 33:36.638
I'm just taking down
a few notes for the article.

33:37.838 --> 33:39.706
How'd you find out
I was here?

33:39.708 --> 33:42.976
Um, I just got told that
you worked on a fruit stand

33:42.978 --> 33:44.911
on a street corner
in downtown.

33:44.913 --> 33:46.249
So I took
my chances.

33:47.282 --> 33:49.282
I started walking around,
hoping I'd find you,

33:49.284 --> 33:50.920
and, um, here you are!

33:56.857 --> 33:58.627
So, uh...

34:00.328 --> 34:02.365
you gonna buy
some mangoes or what?

34:03.999 --> 34:06.235
I'm OK, thanks.

34:07.236 --> 34:08.601
You don't
like mangoes?

34:08.603 --> 34:10.469
They're OK.

34:10.472 --> 34:13.304
I think you should
lay down some cash

34:13.306 --> 34:15.378
and have one of
these delicious treats.

34:16.344 --> 34:17.812
Fresh off the boat.

34:19.748 --> 34:21.280
Sure, OK.

34:21.282 --> 34:22.951
- I'll... I'll have one.
- Hmm.

34:24.353 --> 34:26.552
Does... does
that cover it?

34:26.554 --> 34:28.590
What else you
got in there?

34:30.626 --> 34:32.695
That'll do. Here.

34:35.429 --> 34:37.966
Eat one. Hmm?

34:41.902 --> 34:43.271
Put it in.

34:52.713 --> 34:54.416
Chew it.

34:57.918 --> 34:59.821
Slower.

35:03.525 --> 35:04.923
Mm-hmm.

35:06.594 --> 35:08.394
- Bag of mangoes, please.
- Yeah.

35:08.396 --> 35:09.896
- The mangoes fresh?
- Absolutely!

35:10.898 --> 35:11.833
How much for a bag?

35:12.668 --> 35:13.900
- $2. Just mangoes?
- Just mangoes.

35:13.902 --> 35:16.036
- You got a sweet tooth?
- Yeah.

35:16.038 --> 35:18.505
All right.
Enjoy! Stay healthy.

35:18.507 --> 35:21.309
Did you, um...

35:22.077 --> 35:23.913
Did you remarry?

35:25.813 --> 35:28.483
You think I
killed her, don't you?

35:29.451 --> 35:30.916
No, I don't.

35:30.918 --> 35:32.619
I don't know
anything about it.

35:32.621 --> 35:35.421
But you read about it.

35:35.423 --> 35:36.858
Yeah, a little.

35:37.958 --> 35:39.958
So, you want
to interview me,

35:39.960 --> 35:42.528
and you don't want to
talk about that?

35:42.530 --> 35:45.097
You said you didn't
want to talk about that.

35:45.099 --> 35:47.402
You fucking with me, kid?

35:48.903 --> 35:51.641
No, I swear!

35:54.576 --> 35:56.278
I didn't do it.

35:59.114 --> 36:00.750
OK.

36:17.465 --> 36:18.831
Hey!

36:18.833 --> 36:21.770
Hi! What have you been up to?

36:22.771 --> 36:24.537
Oh, a little bit of this,

36:24.539 --> 36:25.704
a little bit of that.

36:25.706 --> 36:26.675
What are you doing?

36:27.742 --> 36:29.809
Cigarettes and laundry.

36:29.811 --> 36:33.548
- Sounds like fun.
- Tons.

36:35.016 --> 36:36.615
Can I join you?

36:36.617 --> 36:39.054
Yes, you shall.

36:41.789 --> 36:45.992
Why do laundry if you're gonna
just end it all in a few weeks?

36:45.994 --> 36:48.561
I'm civilized,
and I like clean stuff.

36:49.864 --> 36:51.865
Don't you have
a mother back home

36:51.867 --> 36:53.032
who's worried about you?

36:53.034 --> 36:54.867
She's always worried about me.

36:54.869 --> 36:58.604
Have you told her about
what your father did,

36:58.606 --> 37:01.840
that you have
a half-brother?

37:01.842 --> 37:05.114
I don't know if it's anything
she even needs to know.

37:06.081 --> 37:07.613
It would crush her.

37:07.615 --> 37:09.782
She... she loved
my father very much.

37:09.784 --> 37:11.619
She respected him.

37:15.690 --> 37:18.023
She ever
tell you that,

37:18.025 --> 37:21.096
that she loves
and respects him?

37:26.835 --> 37:30.903
She was in love with him.

37:30.905 --> 37:33.576
Well, love is
a tricky thing.

37:34.543 --> 37:36.579
It can be pretty deceiving.

37:39.079 --> 37:40.914
You never wonder?

37:40.916 --> 37:42.916
Wonder what?

37:42.918 --> 37:44.920
Well, if it
was real or not.

37:46.121 --> 37:48.153
Well, I've been
trying to go through

37:48.155 --> 37:50.690
these moments in my head,

37:50.692 --> 37:52.795
images of my
parents, um...

37:54.128 --> 37:57.796
things my father said
to me through the years,

37:57.798 --> 38:01.503
things he's said
to my mother.

38:04.639 --> 38:07.907
And my mom can't ever
know about this.

38:07.909 --> 38:11.012
Shouldn't she know
the truth about him?

38:13.248 --> 38:15.951
Sometimes, it's
better not to know.

38:19.920 --> 38:23.658
Could you see yourself being
married to the same person...

38:24.759 --> 38:29.061
for, like, 30,
40, 50 years?

38:29.063 --> 38:31.900
So daunting to
think about it.

38:33.601 --> 38:35.503
I can
picture it.

38:37.005 --> 38:38.941
I just, um...

38:40.275 --> 38:42.575
can't imagine
being in a marriage

38:42.577 --> 38:45.181
with someone I wasn't
madly in love with.

38:48.516 --> 38:50.983
Could you hand me my thong?

38:50.985 --> 38:53.119
It dropped next
to your leg.

39:05.666 --> 39:07.566
Kate...

39:07.568 --> 39:09.135
Yeah?

39:09.137 --> 39:11.974
If you fell in love
with someone...

39:13.775 --> 39:16.077
madly in love
with someone...

39:18.780 --> 39:21.880
would that make life
worth living more?

39:21.882 --> 39:25.017
So, you're saying
if I met this man

39:25.019 --> 39:29.722
and fell deeply, madly,
passionately in love with him

39:29.724 --> 39:31.990
in the next week and a half,

39:31.992 --> 39:34.894
would I decide
not to kill myself?

39:34.896 --> 39:36.499
Yes.

39:39.300 --> 39:41.103
I'd take him with me.

39:44.338 --> 39:47.639
You coming here
has shaken me up a bit.

39:47.641 --> 39:50.075
But I am glad
you decided to stay

39:50.077 --> 39:52.612
instead of going behind my back

39:52.614 --> 39:55.315
and tracking down
my mother's killer.

39:57.851 --> 39:59.788
Me too.

40:00.889 --> 40:02.591
You again?

40:03.358 --> 40:04.791
I have a, uh...

40:04.793 --> 40:07.327
I have a few more
questions for you,

40:07.329 --> 40:08.961
if you're not
gonna mind.

40:10.699 --> 40:12.932
Hey, man,
why should I mind?

40:12.934 --> 40:15.004
All I got is time!
You want a taste?

40:16.371 --> 40:18.139
I do!

40:23.978 --> 40:27.847
- Oh, that's good!
- Mm-hmm.

40:27.849 --> 40:32.021
Um, I do have a few
questions about your family.

40:33.288 --> 40:35.220
Do they live
around here?

40:35.222 --> 40:38.324
Family. Let's see...
Oh, right, for your article.

40:38.326 --> 40:39.958
Yeah.

40:39.960 --> 40:42.330
Getting personal
now, are we?

40:44.065 --> 40:46.965
I haven't seen my
mother since I was 17,

40:46.967 --> 40:49.267
and, uh, I never
had the pleasure

40:49.269 --> 40:51.970
of being introduced
to the old man.

40:51.972 --> 40:53.940
I'm sorry
to hear that.

40:53.942 --> 40:55.340
Sorry? About what?

40:55.342 --> 40:57.744
That you never got
to know your father.

40:59.114 --> 41:00.849
I'm not!

41:03.784 --> 41:05.017
And your mother?

41:05.019 --> 41:06.956
Why... why haven't
you seen her?

41:08.155 --> 41:12.025
She used to do
the beauty-pageant circuit

41:12.027 --> 41:14.229
when she was
a teenager.

41:15.797 --> 41:18.898
She was a troubled
woman later in life,

41:18.900 --> 41:21.103
something wrong
in her brain.

41:22.070 --> 41:24.807
I feel sorry
for her, actually.

41:27.708 --> 41:28.874
Right.

41:32.179 --> 41:34.349
Do you have
any siblings?

41:35.315 --> 41:37.619
Nope.

41:40.454 --> 41:42.690
Do you talk to
Kate anymore?

41:43.925 --> 41:46.028
You've really
done your homework.

41:47.061 --> 41:49.795
I haven't seen her
in a long time.

41:49.797 --> 41:51.396
How come?

41:51.398 --> 41:53.868
You know how
these things are.

41:54.969 --> 41:56.269
Yeah.

41:57.938 --> 42:00.273
Well, um, don't
you miss her?

42:01.943 --> 42:06.749
Yeah, sometimes, when I'm
lying in bed late at night.

42:08.215 --> 42:12.286
She gave me the
best head I've ever had.

42:14.489 --> 42:17.126
You wouldn't
fucking believe it!

42:21.929 --> 42:23.132
Hey!

42:24.833 --> 42:26.833
How was your morning?

42:26.835 --> 42:30.503
- Oh, fine.
- Mmm.

42:30.505 --> 42:31.907
What are you up to?

42:33.041 --> 42:34.941
I'm gonna take a shower.

42:34.943 --> 42:37.079
You want to join me?

42:41.849 --> 42:44.349
<i>♪♪ I know you, brother ♪</i>

42:44.351 --> 42:47.220
<i>♪ You've been taking ♪</i>

42:47.222 --> 42:50.088
<i>♪ I know you, sister ♪</i>

42:50.090 --> 42:54.762
<i>♪ You're trying to make it
for love ♪</i>

42:56.431 --> 42:59.398
<i>♪ How do you feel now? ♪♪</i>

43:05.405 --> 43:07.974
Kate, we need to talk.

43:07.976 --> 43:11.276
♪♪ Sean, come take
a shower with me ♪

43:11.278 --> 43:15.113
♪ Get in here
Get in here ♪

43:23.157 --> 43:24.960
♪ Get in here ♪♪

43:29.030 --> 43:31.066
Hmm.

43:37.137 --> 43:38.840
Oh!

43:47.047 --> 43:49.817
You have, um, really
good water pressure.

43:51.585 --> 43:54.387
That's what you're
thinking about right now?

43:54.389 --> 43:55.387
Mm-hmm.

43:56.391 --> 43:57.990
Amongst other things.

43:57.992 --> 44:00.394
What did you
want to talk about?

44:13.007 --> 44:16.244
- What's the matter?
- Nothing.

44:17.277 --> 44:19.345
Why did you stop?

44:19.347 --> 44:22.447
I'm just a little bit
nervous. That's all.

44:22.449 --> 44:24.986
Don't worry so much.

44:37.297 --> 44:38.399
Oh...

44:39.367 --> 44:41.467
Are you serious?

44:41.469 --> 44:44.470
Hmm. How about I wash
your hair or something?

44:44.472 --> 44:47.373
How about you get
the fuck out of my shower?

44:47.375 --> 44:50.943
What?
What the fuck?

44:50.945 --> 44:53.081
Hey, no, wait!

44:54.181 --> 44:55.914
Wait! Can we talk?

44:55.916 --> 44:57.048
No!

44:57.050 --> 44:58.483
But I need to
talk to you.

44:58.485 --> 45:00.253
- Don't touch me!
- I'm sorry.

45:00.255 --> 45:02.220
Get out
of my house!

45:02.222 --> 45:06.360
- Please!
- Go! Get the fuck out!

45:08.528 --> 45:11.097
- Fine!
- Wait!

45:11.099 --> 45:14.236
- What?
- Drop the towel.

45:15.670 --> 45:18.574
- Are you serious?
- It's my favourite towel.

45:20.275 --> 45:22.407
You are one crazy...

45:58.713 --> 46:00.579
I'm not
letting you in.

46:00.581 --> 46:02.483
I don't want
to come in.

46:45.559 --> 46:48.461
I'm glad I didn't
go and see Henry.

46:48.463 --> 46:51.199
I think if I ever
met him, I...

46:52.367 --> 46:54.002
I would kill him.

47:00.273 --> 47:02.277
I'm gonna go change.

47:04.579 --> 47:07.345
I'll be here,

47:07.347 --> 47:12.385
waiting patiently
for you to return.

47:28.135 --> 47:30.972
<i>"Birds Do the Strangest Things."</i>

47:57.697 --> 48:00.469
Oh! Uh...

48:02.170 --> 48:03.436
