48:11.512 --> 48:13.179
Want me to
roll you one?

48:13.181 --> 48:15.349
Uh, sure.
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

48:16.717 --> 48:18.516
Hey...

48:18.518 --> 48:19.717
Hmm?

48:19.719 --> 48:21.854
What's wrong
with you?

48:21.856 --> 48:24.557
Nothing.
Nothing's wrong.

48:24.559 --> 48:25.825
Mmm...

48:25.827 --> 48:27.827
No, I'm just, um...

48:27.829 --> 48:30.862
I was just thinking about
that letter, you know.

48:30.864 --> 48:32.197
Mmm.

48:32.199 --> 48:34.666
Like, who the hell
could have written it?

48:34.668 --> 48:37.436
Do you have, um...
Do you have any idea?

48:37.438 --> 48:39.807
No. I have no idea.

48:41.242 --> 48:43.678
I mean, your guess
is as good as mine.

48:45.213 --> 48:49.384
Hey, I'm hungry!
Let's go get some food.

49:13.673 --> 49:15.740
- So, Kate...
- Hmm?

49:15.742 --> 49:17.709
Look, I need to
ask you something...

49:17.711 --> 49:20.748
Hey. I wrote the letter.

49:23.550 --> 49:25.483
You may never
want to see me again,

49:25.485 --> 49:26.885
and I'll understand that.

49:26.887 --> 49:29.220
So, what? This whole
thing's been a lie?

49:29.222 --> 49:31.356
Just let me explain, OK?

49:31.358 --> 49:33.626
Well, tell me!
Enlighten me into your psyche.

49:33.628 --> 49:35.394
- OK, I'm...
- The truth.

49:35.396 --> 49:37.463
- Yes, of course.
- No more lies.

49:37.465 --> 49:38.567
No more lies.

49:40.601 --> 49:42.267
I wrote you the letter

49:42.269 --> 49:44.769
because I wanted to
lure you over here

49:44.771 --> 49:47.940
and seduce you
into falling in love with me

49:47.942 --> 49:51.579
so I could convince you
to kill him, to kill Henry.

49:53.213 --> 49:55.748
What does that even mean?
What are you telling me?

49:55.750 --> 49:57.516
I thought that
if you fell for me

49:57.518 --> 49:59.552
and you knew that
he murdered my mother,

49:59.554 --> 50:01.322
you'd want to
help me get revenge.

50:02.489 --> 50:04.423
Do you know how
crazy that sounds?

50:04.425 --> 50:06.691
Well, now that I'm
the one falling for you,

50:06.693 --> 50:08.927
I can't go through
with it, so...

50:08.929 --> 50:10.528
You are? You're...

50:10.530 --> 50:13.601
Falling for you?
Completely.

50:17.572 --> 50:19.405
This doesn't make any sense.

50:19.407 --> 50:21.840
Why would you write me a letter
and lure me down here,

50:21.842 --> 50:24.677
but when I get down here,
you convince me not to see him?

50:24.679 --> 50:26.412
Henry's a very
convincing guy.

50:26.414 --> 50:28.546
I knew if you
met him, he would...

50:28.548 --> 50:30.682
You know, you
wouldn't believe me.

50:30.684 --> 50:32.284
Oh, I should
believe you now?

50:32.286 --> 50:33.651
Yes.

50:33.653 --> 50:35.253
OK, but why me?

50:35.255 --> 50:36.988
Why not get someone
else to kill him?

50:36.990 --> 50:39.557
- Motive.
- Why would I have a motive?

50:39.559 --> 50:41.961
Your recently deceased father
was having an affair

50:41.963 --> 50:43.394
and had a
secret family.

50:43.396 --> 50:45.396
You'd have motive
to want to kill the child

50:45.398 --> 50:46.567
that was a result
of that affair.

50:48.369 --> 50:49.934
I can't fucking believe
that you wanted me to kill him,

50:49.936 --> 50:51.470
or anyone
for that matter.

50:51.472 --> 50:53.005
That man fucking
killed my mother!

50:53.007 --> 50:55.673
- Yeah, I know. But...
- But what?

50:55.675 --> 50:58.276
It doesn't mean you have
the right to murder him.

50:58.278 --> 50:59.979
I mean, OK, he might
have deserved it.

50:59.981 --> 51:02.748
And if that was my mother,
I might want to do the same.

51:02.750 --> 51:04.316
So, what are
you saying?

51:04.318 --> 51:05.985
If you're so set
on killing yourself,

51:05.987 --> 51:07.552
why wouldn't you
just kill him?

51:07.554 --> 51:09.621
Believe me, that was
my first instinct,

51:09.623 --> 51:11.990
to just kill that
asshole myself.

51:11.992 --> 51:14.360
But, on the off chance
that I got caught,

51:14.362 --> 51:17.329
I wouldn't be able to execute
my suicide as planned.

51:17.331 --> 51:19.300
Oh, fuck!
You're insane.

51:22.369 --> 51:24.672
I just want what
he has coming to him.

51:26.507 --> 51:28.840
- I'm gonna go.
- Hey, don't go!

51:28.842 --> 51:31.744
Well, I'm going.
I need to figure shit out.

51:31.746 --> 51:34.847
Please, I'm sorry.
I... I didn't mean to lie to you.

51:34.849 --> 51:36.481
Sean!

51:48.862 --> 51:54.235
<i>♪♪ I feel my brain begin
to swirl and scatter ♪</i>

51:55.936 --> 52:00.775
<i>♪ Haze has occluded my eyes ♪</i>

52:02.576 --> 52:08.514
<i>♪ I know that all this
doesn't really matter ♪</i>

52:08.516 --> 52:14.519
♪ When I'm drowning
in my river of lies ♪

52:14.521 --> 52:19.490
♪ Here comes the battle
for my mind ♪

52:19.492 --> 52:22.961
♪ But will she be cruel? ♪

52:22.963 --> 52:26.334
♪ Will she be kind? ♪

52:27.735 --> 52:32.340
<i>♪ I will no longer live in... ♪♪</i>

52:43.851 --> 52:45.583
I like your sign.

52:45.585 --> 52:49.623
Thank you. I was hoping
it would be romantic.

52:50.590 --> 52:52.527
Mission accomplished.

52:54.661 --> 52:56.994
You look tired.

52:56.996 --> 53:00.099
Yeah. I couldn't sleep
at all last night.

53:00.101 --> 53:02.037
Me either.

53:04.739 --> 53:06.907
You should quit those,
you know.

53:14.014 --> 53:15.817
Let me have a drag.

53:26.025 --> 53:28.092
How do you think
I'd do in prison?

53:29.597 --> 53:31.599
What a defeatist
attitude.

53:33.067 --> 53:35.867
You don't think you
can get away with it?

53:38.505 --> 53:40.505
- Let's get out of here.
- OK.

53:40.507 --> 53:42.476
Should we get
something to eat?

53:43.510 --> 53:44.945
Definitely!

53:50.050 --> 53:53.588
<i>Have you ever been
to a masquerade ball?</i>

55:05.125 --> 55:07.191
Good morning!

55:07.193 --> 55:09.827
I woke up, and you
weren't next to me.

55:09.829 --> 55:11.729
I thought you'd left.

55:11.731 --> 55:14.101
- You OK?
- I'm fine.

55:19.773 --> 55:21.675
Have you
been crying?

55:23.643 --> 55:25.110
Yeah.

55:25.112 --> 55:28.450
How come?
Wh-what's wrong?

55:31.684 --> 55:33.188
I don't know.

55:41.295 --> 55:44.097
Last night
was so much fun.

55:45.164 --> 55:47.231
Maybe we could do
something today.

55:47.233 --> 55:51.603
We could go somewhere
neither of us have been before.

55:53.873 --> 55:58.212
I... I don't want to
do anything today, OK?

56:01.648 --> 56:03.217
Are you upset with me?

56:09.856 --> 56:12.092
You can go if you want to.

56:14.061 --> 56:15.697
I get it.

56:23.804 --> 56:26.106
You mind if I
just sit with you?

57:00.840 --> 57:05.376
<i>♪♪ Your mouth
covered in sand ♪</i>

57:05.378 --> 57:08.815
<i>♪ As you washed up
on the beach ♪</i>

57:10.317 --> 57:13.985
<i>♪ You live in
a burial ground ♪</i>

57:19.259 --> 57:22.193
<i>♪ Collecting stones ♪</i>

57:22.195 --> 57:24.963
<i>♪ Traded like gold ♪</i>

57:24.965 --> 57:27.969
<i>♪ As you walk
with your two feet ♪</i>

57:29.036 --> 57:31.403
<i>♪ Collecting stones ♪</i>

57:31.405 --> 57:34.206
<i>♪ Traded like gold ♪</i>

57:34.208 --> 57:37.345
<i>♪ As you walk
with your two feet ♪</i>

57:43.650 --> 57:46.721
<i>♪ The devil's sentence stays ♪</i>

57:53.092 --> 57:58.229
<i>♪ The devil's sentence stays
The devil's sentence stays ♪</i>

57:58.231 --> 58:03.769
<i>♪ The devil's sentence stays
The devil's sentence stays ♪♪</i>

58:41.074 --> 58:43.041
<i>Hey, Kate!</i>

58:43.043 --> 58:46.780
<i>It's Mom.
Are you there? Kate?</i>

59:00.159 --> 59:02.927
Hey! Hey, wake up.

59:05.231 --> 59:07.932
- What?
- I can't sleep.

59:07.934 --> 59:11.336
I need to talk to you
about something.

59:11.338 --> 59:12.970
What time is it?

59:12.972 --> 59:15.043
I don't know.
It's late.

59:16.876 --> 59:19.279
Let's go and get
something to eat.

59:20.514 --> 59:22.150
OK.

59:29.389 --> 59:31.025
Hey...

59:34.460 --> 59:36.394
I was thinking
about what you said,

59:36.396 --> 59:38.362
about wanting me to kill Henry.

59:38.364 --> 59:40.434
What about it?

59:42.436 --> 59:44.135
I want to do it.

59:44.137 --> 59:45.440
What?

59:46.873 --> 59:48.940
Henry murdered
your mother.

59:48.942 --> 59:50.474
The guy
deserves it.

59:50.476 --> 59:53.478
He deserves to die,
and I want to do it.

59:53.480 --> 59:55.349
I want to
do it for you.

59:56.449 --> 59:58.516
Are you fucking with me?

59:58.518 --> 01:00:01.054
No, I'm
totally serious.

01:00:05.291 --> 01:00:06.992
OK, well, why the change?

01:00:06.994 --> 01:00:08.526
Don't you agree it's insane?

01:00:08.528 --> 01:00:11.396
I mean, you're a lot of things,
but you're not a killer.

01:00:11.398 --> 01:00:13.865
Yeah, you're right,
I'm not a killer,

01:00:13.867 --> 01:00:16.568
but I've also never felt
this way about anyone before.

01:00:16.570 --> 01:00:18.103
People change.

01:00:18.105 --> 01:00:19.970
People do crazy things,

01:00:19.972 --> 01:00:22.342
things they never could
have imagined doing.

01:00:27.280 --> 01:00:29.313
This is what
you wanted, right?

01:00:29.315 --> 01:00:31.115
It's what you
were planning.

01:00:31.117 --> 01:00:32.284
Yeah, but...

01:00:32.286 --> 01:00:34.885
Well, let's just
stick to the plan.

01:00:34.887 --> 01:00:36.454
It was a crazy plan.

01:00:36.456 --> 01:00:39.227
Well, I'm in
a crazy kind of mood.

01:00:40.260 --> 01:00:42.028
You're being ridiculous.

01:00:43.831 --> 01:00:46.530
You don't think I'm capable
of going through with it.

01:00:46.532 --> 01:00:50.003
I'm not saying that.
I just don't know if...

01:00:51.070 --> 01:00:52.436
You'll get caught.

01:00:52.438 --> 01:00:54.107
I've got this.

01:00:58.478 --> 01:01:01.079
So, how are you
gonna do it exactly?

01:01:01.081 --> 01:01:02.313
Shoot him.

01:01:02.315 --> 01:01:04.548
- Shoot him?
- Yeah.

01:01:06.085 --> 01:01:07.854
You know,
with a gun.

01:01:10.556 --> 01:01:13.191
Well, do you
even have a gun?

01:01:13.193 --> 01:01:15.329
No, I need to go buy one.

01:01:16.896 --> 01:01:19.597
OK, sure.
Go get a gun and shoot him.

01:01:21.068 --> 01:01:23.101
Hey, I'm offering up
my services.

01:01:25.972 --> 01:01:27.905
I... You're crazy.

01:01:29.342 --> 01:01:31.976
Blah! I'm fucking crazy!

01:01:31.978 --> 01:01:34.211
I'm a fucking nutter!
And I'm gonna do it.

01:02:02.175 --> 01:02:04.508
Where did you get a gun?

01:02:04.510 --> 01:02:07.211
From a shady gun dealer guy.

01:02:07.213 --> 01:02:09.916
He even threw in
some free bullets.

01:02:13.219 --> 01:02:14.653
Now I just need to figure out

01:02:14.655 --> 01:02:16.521
how to execute
the perfect murder.

01:02:16.523 --> 01:02:20.258
Sean, have you ever
even shot a gun?

01:02:21.427 --> 01:02:22.661
How hard could it be?

01:02:22.663 --> 01:02:25.362
This guy said this is
really easy to handle.

01:02:25.364 --> 01:02:27.965
It's just a point and
a shoot type of deal.

01:02:27.967 --> 01:02:32.003
I thought about using a blade,
but that would be too messy.

01:02:32.005 --> 01:02:34.139
You're not serious?
This is crazy!

01:02:34.141 --> 01:02:38.079
No. I'm willing
to do anything for you.

01:02:42.315 --> 01:02:43.951
OK.

01:02:57.496 --> 01:02:59.000
You know...

01:03:00.000 --> 01:03:01.298
I'm pretty impressed

01:03:01.300 --> 01:03:03.971
you actually went out
and bought a gun.

01:03:05.739 --> 01:03:08.175
It's kind of bad-ass.

01:03:10.210 --> 01:03:13.380
Well, you're
bringing it out of me.

01:03:15.014 --> 01:03:17.014
So, what's the plan?

01:03:17.016 --> 01:03:19.684
Well, I've come up
with something

01:03:19.686 --> 01:03:22.220
totally elaborate and genius.

01:03:22.222 --> 01:03:23.688
Mm-hmm.

01:03:23.690 --> 01:03:26.027
I'm gonna follow him.

01:03:27.626 --> 01:03:31.666
And then I'll corner him in
a hidden alley somewhere nearby.

01:03:33.300 --> 01:03:38.339
And then I'll shoot him
in the back of his fucking head.

01:03:41.108 --> 01:03:43.144
What do you think?

01:03:45.445 --> 01:03:47.414
I think it'll work.

01:03:49.016 --> 01:03:50.648
You got any bananas?

01:03:50.650 --> 01:03:53.688
No. If you want fruit, go
to the fucking grocery store!

01:03:54.788 --> 01:03:56.588
Uh, two mangoes.

01:03:56.590 --> 01:03:59.490
Get out
of here. Go!

01:03:59.492 --> 01:04:01.728
Jesus Christ!

01:04:11.605 --> 01:04:13.641
Are you ready for this?

01:04:15.409 --> 01:04:17.608
Ready as
I'll ever be.

01:04:17.610 --> 01:04:19.313
You brought the gun?

01:04:20.347 --> 01:04:22.216
I've got it.

01:04:24.818 --> 01:04:26.383
What about
the gunshot?

01:04:26.385 --> 01:04:29.253
When the gun goes off,
people are gonna hear it.

01:04:29.255 --> 01:04:30.621
What if there
are witnesses?

01:04:30.623 --> 01:04:32.657
That's why you've
gotta be my lookout.

01:04:32.659 --> 01:04:35.526
Signal me if you see
someone loafing about,

01:04:35.528 --> 01:04:36.661
and I'll back away.

01:04:36.663 --> 01:04:38.599
Plus, it's late.
Look, nobody's around.

01:04:40.833 --> 01:04:44.135
- You don't know that.
- Yeah, I don't.

01:04:44.137 --> 01:04:46.271
But if something weird happens,
I'll improvise.

01:04:46.273 --> 01:04:48.409
What about the body?

01:04:50.577 --> 01:04:52.142
What about it?

01:04:52.144 --> 01:04:54.545
What are gonna do with it
after you've killed him?

01:04:54.547 --> 01:04:56.414
Nothing. We're just
gonna leave him.

01:04:56.416 --> 01:04:58.682
What?

01:04:58.684 --> 01:05:02.088
I don't think there's anything
wrong with leaving the body.

01:05:04.824 --> 01:05:07.093
Why are you
doing this?

01:05:08.228 --> 01:05:10.030
Why?

01:05:10.864 --> 01:05:12.666
You know why.

01:05:13.666 --> 01:05:15.369
No, I don't.

01:05:16.335 --> 01:05:17.771
Not really.

01:05:20.239 --> 01:05:21.508
He's leaving.

01:05:22.476 --> 01:05:25.443
OK, this is it.

01:05:25.445 --> 01:05:26.680
Are you...

01:05:35.621 --> 01:05:38.322
Henry.

01:05:44.164 --> 01:05:45.729
Stop! Stop.

01:05:45.731 --> 01:05:47.231
What... what
are you doing?

01:05:47.233 --> 01:05:48.599
I can't let
you do this!

01:05:48.601 --> 01:05:50.501
- Kate?
- Hey.

01:05:50.503 --> 01:05:53.470
Look, I lied to you
about everything, OK?

01:05:53.472 --> 01:05:55.340
He's not your
half-brother.

01:05:55.342 --> 01:05:56.740
What?

01:05:56.742 --> 01:05:58.610
You told him I'm
his half-brother?

01:05:58.612 --> 01:05:59.776
- Yes.
- Hey, fuck this!

01:05:59.778 --> 01:06:01.347
No, don't touch me!

01:06:02.916 --> 01:06:05.383
He's just this guy
I used to date.

01:06:05.385 --> 01:06:07.217
Henry's your
ex-boyfriend?

01:06:07.219 --> 01:06:08.288
Yes.

01:06:10.190 --> 01:06:13.191
But the murder trial.
This guy killed your mother.

01:06:13.193 --> 01:06:15.726
Well, he really was
on trial for killing a woman.

01:06:15.728 --> 01:06:17.795
It... it just wasn't my mother.

01:06:17.797 --> 01:06:20.365
You told this guy
I killed your mother?

01:06:20.367 --> 01:06:21.798
Yes, OK? Sorry!

01:06:21.800 --> 01:06:24.235
This is so fucked up.
Why do you have a gun?

01:06:24.237 --> 01:06:26.604
- He was gonna kill you!
- What?

01:06:26.606 --> 01:06:28.509
I wasn't really
gonna do it.

01:06:29.742 --> 01:06:32.242
I knew that you
were lying to me.

01:06:32.244 --> 01:06:33.279
I was just
calling your bluff.

01:06:35.215 --> 01:06:37.749
I even did the research
on this guy, on the trial.

01:06:37.751 --> 01:06:39.650
Your parents
aren't even dead.

01:06:39.652 --> 01:06:41.219
I found the speech
that I wrote

01:06:41.221 --> 01:06:42.920
for my father's funeral
in your house.

01:06:42.922 --> 01:06:44.889
You've been lying
to me this entire time!

01:06:44.891 --> 01:06:46.925
And could everyone
just calm the fuck down!

01:06:46.927 --> 01:06:48.659
This thing isn't
even loaded. Look.

01:06:50.697 --> 01:06:52.262
That wasn't
meant to happen.

01:06:52.264 --> 01:06:54.532
There might have been
something in the chamber.

01:06:54.534 --> 01:06:56.700
There's... This was
a mistake. I swear.

01:06:56.702 --> 01:06:59.269
You guys are
both psychotic.

01:06:59.271 --> 01:07:00.938
I should
call the cops.

01:07:00.940 --> 01:07:02.807
No! No, no, no.
Don't do that.

01:07:02.809 --> 01:07:05.409
He's right. There's
no need to call the cops.

01:07:05.411 --> 01:07:07.545
This is just a big
misunderstanding.

01:07:07.547 --> 01:07:09.680
I'm getting the
hell out of here.

01:07:09.682 --> 01:07:11.282
Let's go, Kate.

01:07:11.284 --> 01:07:12.684
I'm not
coming with you!

01:07:12.686 --> 01:07:13.653
Fine!

01:07:14.621 --> 01:07:16.688
I've gotta go.

01:07:16.690 --> 01:07:18.655
Sean. Wait!

01:07:20.427 --> 01:07:22.930
I guess I'll see you
on the other side.

01:07:24.797 --> 01:07:26.731
Oh, what?
The whole suicide thing?

01:07:26.733 --> 01:07:28.432
I don't know a lot
about anything,

01:07:28.434 --> 01:07:30.436
but I know you're not
gonna kill yourself.

01:07:31.670 --> 01:07:33.604
You came to my father's
funeral, though.

01:07:33.606 --> 01:07:34.972
That was real.

01:07:34.974 --> 01:07:37.307
I'm still trying
to figure out

01:07:37.309 --> 01:07:40.311
what kind of a sick
person would do that,

01:07:40.313 --> 01:07:43.847
to screw with someone
in their weakest moment.

01:07:43.849 --> 01:07:47.253
A really, really
fucked-up person.

01:07:48.655 --> 01:07:52.593
You're an original.
I'll give you that much.

01:07:54.628 --> 01:07:58.265
No! No, I take that back.

01:07:59.032 --> 01:08:01.335
You're a fucking cliché!

01:08:24.858 --> 01:08:26.894
<i>My whole life is a lie.</i>

01:08:33.300 --> 01:08:35.868
<i>Falling for you?</i>

01:08:37.002 --> 01:08:38.770
<i>Completely.</i>

01:10:21.740 --> 01:10:23.676
Kate?

01:10:31.650 --> 01:10:33.354
Kate?

01:10:47.065 --> 01:10:49.502
Kate?

01:11:05.685 --> 01:11:08.856
Uh, hi.
It's me. Um...

01:11:10.457 --> 01:11:12.790
Uh, I'm... I'm...
I'm at the house.

01:11:12.792 --> 01:11:15.759
Could you call me
when you get this, please?

01:11:15.761 --> 01:11:19.465
Uh, thanks. OK. Bye.

01:11:32.645 --> 01:11:35.245
Hey! Can I help you?

01:11:35.247 --> 01:11:37.915
Oh, I'm... I'm just looking
for my friend Kate.

01:11:37.917 --> 01:11:39.420
She lives up
in this house.

01:11:44.056 --> 01:11:46.760
Sir, no one named Kate
lives in that house.

01:11:48.161 --> 01:11:49.927
What do you mean?

01:11:49.929 --> 01:11:51.928
The house is on the market.

01:11:51.930 --> 01:11:53.900
No one's lived there
for the last 4 months.

01:11:56.869 --> 01:12:00.537
N-no, it isn't.
What are you talking about?

01:12:00.539 --> 01:12:02.607
I was here recently.
You've seen me here.

01:12:02.609 --> 01:12:04.709
I've never seen you
in my life.

01:12:04.711 --> 01:12:06.210
Yes, you have.

01:12:06.212 --> 01:12:09.112
You waved to me once when you
were throwing your trash out.

01:12:09.114 --> 01:12:10.947
I don't know
what to tell you, pal.

01:12:10.949 --> 01:12:12.051
But you got
the wrong guy.

01:12:13.152 --> 01:12:16.056
I gotta get to work.
Take it easy!

01:12:26.198 --> 01:12:27.533
You're here!

01:12:29.167 --> 01:12:31.471
Hi!

01:12:33.171 --> 01:12:35.475
Hey.

01:12:36.943 --> 01:12:38.679
You came back.

01:12:43.082 --> 01:12:44.952
Just in time.

01:12:46.118 --> 01:12:47.884
You moved out?

01:12:47.886 --> 01:12:51.155
Yeah. Packed up all my junk
and I'm headed out of here.

01:12:51.157 --> 01:12:53.624
I just had a run-in
with your neighbour.

01:12:53.626 --> 01:12:55.192
